<p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-size:14px;"><a href="https://www.cityofforsyth.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Statement-regarding-city-bldg-closures.pdf" target="_blank">Click here for full text version</a></span></strong></p>
